credits.category.team=Core Team
credits.category.team.detail=The core team is responsible for the overall direction, maintenance and release of GT New Horizons.\nTheir work spans design, coordination, infrastructure and long-term vision for the pack.

credits.category.dev=Developers
credits.category.dev.detail=Developers design and implement the mods, scripts, configs and tooling that make GT New Horizons possible.\nThis includes everything from new gameplay systems to build pipeline improvements.

credits.category.contrib=Contributors
credits.category.contrib.detail=Contributors have submitted fixes, content or improvements that found their way into the pack. Every contribution matters.

credits.category.support=Supporters
credits.category.support.detail=Supporters have helped keep the project going through donations, hosting, moderation and other forms of community support. We are grateful for their generosity and dedication.

credits.category.thanks=Special Thanks
credits.category.thanks.detail=Special thanks to everyone who reported bugs, wrote documentation, created guides or supported the project in ways big and small.\nGT New Horizons would not exist without its community.

