# Test category: id "Indexed Detail" -> sanitized indexed_detail
# Indexes are defined out of order here (0, 10, 2) to verify natural sort renders them 0, 2, 10.
# \n within a paragraph = line break only (no empty-line gap between lines of the same paragraph).
credits.category.indexed_detail.detail.0=Paragraph zero, first line.\nParagraph zero, second line (line break, no gap above).
credits.category.indexed_detail.detail.2=Paragraph two (natural sort: renders after 0, before 10).
credits.category.indexed_detail.detail.10=Paragraph ten (natural sort: renders last despite "10" > "2" lexicographically).